CONTACT_FORM_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Have questions or need support? We're here to help you crush your fitness goals!
CONTACT_FORM_TEXT_FIELD_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: How can we assist you today?
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does GymMate help me achieve my fitness goals?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: GymMate provides personalized workout plans, tracks your progress, and offers expert guidance to help you reach your fitness goals efficiently and effectively.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Absolutely! GymMate caters to all fitness levels, from beginners to advanced gym-goers. Our app offers tailored workouts and instructional videos to ensure a safe and productive gym experience for everyone.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I use GymMate at any fitness center?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, GymMate is designed to be used at any gym or fitness center. Our extensive exercise database and customizable workout plans adapt to the equipment available at your chosen facility.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How does GymMate track my progress?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: GymMate uses advanced algorithms to monitor your workout data, including sets, reps, and weights. It provides visual progress reports, performance analytics, and achievement milestones to keep you motivated and on track.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our gym app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the app help me with my gym routine?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides personalized workout plans, tracks your progress, and offers video tutorials for proper exercise form, helping you maximize your gym sessions and reach your fitness goals faster.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I use the app at any gym?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! Our app is designed to work with any gym equipment and can even suggest bodyweight alternatives when needed. It's perfect for use at home, in your local gym, or while traveling.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How does the app track my progress?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: The app allows you to log your workouts, including sets, reps, and weights. It then generates progress charts and provides insights on your improvements over time, helping you stay motivated and on track.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Our app caters to all fitness levels, from beginners to advanced gym-goers. It offers customized workout plans based on your experience, fitness goals, and available time, ensuring a safe and effective fitness journey for everyone.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I connect with other users or a personal trainer through the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Definitely! Our app features a community section where you can connect with other users, share achievements, and participate in challenges. We also offer an option to connect with certified personal trainers for personalized guidance and support.
